Package com.xiantrimble.combinatorics

Interface Summary
Combinatoric<T> The root interface for combinations and permutations.
CombinatoricEngine<T> Combinatoric engines provide access to the state changes that are happening while generating combinations and permutations.
CombinatoricFactory A factory for combination and permutation collections.
CombinatoricHandler<T> An event handler for building a combination or permutation based on changes from the last combination or permutation.
CombinatoricIterator<T> A root interface for combinatoric iterators.
CombMathUtils Math methods for dealing with complex combinatoric problems with duplicates involved.
GroupedDomain<E> A representation of a set of elements where the like elements have been grouped.
 

Class Summary
AbstractCombinatoric<T> An abstract base class for combinatoric implementations.
AbstractCombinatoricEngine<T> An abstract base class for CombinatoricEngine implementations.
AbstractCombinatoricHandler<T> An abstract base for combinatoric handlers.
Combinations<T> A collection class that contains the combinations of a set of elements.
CombinationsEngine<T> A CombinatoricEngine implementation for combinations.
CombinatoricFactoryImpl A basic implementation of the CombinatoricFactory.
CombMathUtilsImpl An implementation of the CombMathUtils.
CombMathUtilsImpl.PartialCombinationCount Defines a partial solution to a counting of combinations.
FastGroupedDomain<E> An implementation of GroupedDomain, based on Javolutions FastList.
IndexBasedPermutations<T>  
IndexBasedPermutationsEngine<T> A CombinatoricEngine implementation for Permutations.
Permutations<T> A collection class that contains the permutations of a set of elements.
PermutationsEngine<T> A CombinatoricEngine implementation for Permutations.
Utils Static utilities to support this package.
